sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant API as Worker API
  participant AI as AI Classifier
  participant Flow as Workflow Engine
  participant Billing as Billing Guard
  participant Exec as Execution Layer
  participant Audit as Audit Log

  User->>API: Submit workflow request
  API->>AI: Classify intent and risk
  AI->>Flow: Return workflow route
  Flow->>Billing: Check entitlement
  Billing-->>Flow: Allowed / requires payment
  Flow->>Exec: Execute approved modules
  Exec->>Audit: Store decision trail
  Audit-->>API: Execution receipt
  API-->>User: Result + status
